title: DayZ Crack [V49.1] {Full Game}
description:
=====================================================================================
DayZ is an open world survival video game in development by Bohemia Interactive and the stand-alone version of the award-winning mod of the same name. The game was test-released on December 16, 2013, for Microsoft Windows via digital distribution platform Steam, and is currently in early alpha testing.

The game places the player in the fictional 225 km2 post-Soviet state of Chernarus, where an mysterious plague has turned most of the population into violent infected called Zeds. As a survivor, the player must scavenge the world for food, water, weapons, and medicine, while killing or avoiding zeds, and killing, avoiding or cooperating with other players in an effort to survive the outbreak
